@startuml Activity - QR Code Scanning Process
!theme plain

title QR Code Scanning (BCE Flow)

|Actor| User
|Boundary| UI (RoomPage)
|Control| RoomController
|Entity| SensorData / DB

|User|
start
:Scan QR Code;

|UI (RoomPage)|
:Request Page Load;

|RoomController|
:Receive Request;
:Call Fetch Data Service;

|SensorData / DB|
:Query Latest Readings;
:Query Historical Data;
:Query Predictions;

|RoomController|
if (Data Valid?) then (yes)
  :Prepare Dashboard Props;
  :Generate Charts;
else (no)
  :Prepare Error Page;
endif

|UI (RoomPage)|
:Render Dashboard Page;
:Display AQI Gauge & Graphs;

|User|
:View Room Status;
stop

@enduml